<section class="rbp-order-confirm">
  <div class="page-width rbp-order-confirm__hero">
    <p class="rbp-order-confirm__eyebrow">Order received</p>
    <h1>Next step: complete your Core Service intake</h1>
    <p>Thanks for purchasing a Core Service. Your order confirmation email contains your Shopify order number. Use that number when completing the intake form.</p>
    <div class="rbp-order-confirm__actions"><a class="button button--primary" href="/pages/core-services-intake">Go to intake hub</a><a class="button button--secondary" href="/collections/core-services">View Core Services</a></div>
  </div>
  <div class="page-width rbp-order-confirm__cards">
    <div><strong>1. Find your order number</strong><p>It appears in the Shopify confirmation email.</p></div>
    <div><strong>2. Choose your service intake</strong><p>Select the form matching the service you purchased.</p></div>
    <div><strong>3. Submit your intake</strong><p>RBP receives the details by email and can match the submission to your order.</p></div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
.rbp-order-confirm{padding:48px 0 72px}.rbp-order-confirm__hero{padding:42px 30px;border-radius:28px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(var(--color-foreground),.06),rgba(var(--color-button),.08));border:1px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground),.08)}.rbp-order-confirm__eyebrow{text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.13em;font-size:1.2rem;color:rgba(var(--color-foreground),.68);margin:0 0 12px}.rbp-order-confirm h1{font-size:clamp(3rem,5vw,5.8rem);line-height:1.02;margin:0}.rbp-order-confirm__hero p{max-width:780px;font-size:1.7rem;color:rgba(var(--color-foreground),.76)}.rbp-order-confirm__actions{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:22px}.rbp-order-confirm__cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr));gap:16px;margin-top:24px}.rbp-order-confirm__cards div{padding:24px;border-radius:22px;border:1px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground),.1);box-shadow:0 10px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.04)}@media(max-width:749px){.rbp-order-confirm__cards{grid-template-columns:1fr}.rbp-order-confirm__hero{padding:28px 20px}}
</style>
